Test in staging environment
  cd vagrant; vagrant up
  ssh 192.168.2.2

Deploy to production environment
  ssh-add credentials/id_rsa
  ansible-playbook -i production site.yml

Manual actions required on first deployment
  Decryption of sensitive files (will be prompted)
  Performing initial ssh login to bwbackup@<backuphost> as user root
    via: backupninja -n -d
    might have to run some commands (e.g. duplicity) manually once
  Running './bridgewalker --initdb' to initialize the database
  Create Bridgewalker configuration file
  Update 'metricsd_host' and redeploy Graphite host
